"{\"uid\": \"localnews8.com-news-2024-08-02-vitriol-about-female-boxer-imane-khelif-fuels-concern-of-backlash-against-lgbtq-and-women-athletes\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Associated Press  PARIS (AP) - LGBTQ+ athletes, officials and observers have warned that a deluge of hateful comments misidentifying a female boxer in the Paris Olympics as transgender or a man could pose dangers for the LGBTQ+ community and female athletes.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 25, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999997839968506, \"rank\": 2.1497461337495671e-07, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Famous figures like former U.S. President Donald Trump and \\\"Harry Potter\\\" author J.K. Rowling have railed against Algerian boxer Imane Khelif after her Italian competitor Angela Carini quit their bout Thursday.\", \"from\": 259, \"to\": 469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 301, \"end\": 313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999969678793189, \"rank\": 1.6181112342859976e-06, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 319, \"end\": 331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\", \"score\": 0.9999110209090105, \"rank\": 8.771931202000558e-05, \"text\": \"Harry Potter\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Harry_Potter\"}, {\"begin\": 340, \"end\": 344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.686029114147703e-12, \"text\": \"J.K.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}, {\"begin\": 373, \"end\": 381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9866951934873442, \"rank\": 0.012018313928983042, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 388, \"end\": 400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 411, \"end\": 418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.999841019592554, \"rank\": 7.878776814178319e-05, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 430, \"end\": 443, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103662667, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some athletes and LGBTQ+ observers worry such comments have already started to vilify transgender, nonbinary and other LGBTQ+ people at an event championing inclusion.\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes as expanding interpretations of gender identity have spurred a larger political tug-of-war, often centered around sports.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 768, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jump to comments \\u2193  KIFI Local News 8 is committed to providing a forum for civil and constructive conversation.\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 790, \"end\": 794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KIFI-TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"KIFI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KIFI-TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KIFI-TV\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please keep your comments respectful and relevant.\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 934, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can review our Community Guidelines byclicking here  If you would like to share a story idea, please submit ithere.\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"EEO Report|Terms of Use|Privacy Policy|Community Guidelines|About Us|KIFI-TV FCC Public File|FCC Applications|  Do Not Sell My Personal Information  Daily News UpdateBreaking News AlertDaily Weather ForecastSevere Weather AlertContests and Promotions\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1306, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1125, \"end\": 1132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KIFI-TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"KIFI-TV\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KIFI-TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KIFI-TV\"}, {\"begin\": 1133, \"end\": 1136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Communications_Commission\", \"score\": 0.999553824391727, \"rank\": 0.00044624304747053535, \"text\": \"FCC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Communications_Commission\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Communications_Commission\"}, {\"begin\": 1137, \"end\": 1148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_file\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Public File\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_file\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Public_file\"}, {\"begin\": 1149, \"end\": 1152, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Communications_Commissio